---
import { CLINIC } from '~/consts';
---

{/* 한의원 신뢰형 hero - 원장 portrait + 깊이 있는 활자. 모바일 우선 반응형. */}
<section class="bg-stone-50 relative overflow-hidden">
  {/* 다층 배경 - 우상단 + 좌하단 green halo + 미세 노이즈 */}
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute -right-40 -top-20 w-[640px] h-[640px] rounded-full bg-green-100/50 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute -left-32 bottom-[-180px] w-[520px] h-[520px] rounded-full bg-deok-100/40 blur-[120px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.025] mix-blend-multiply"
      style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 24px 24px;">
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* fixed overlay header에 hero 첫 픽셀이 가려지지 않도록 상단 여유 */}
  <div class="v-container pt-24 sm:pt-28 md:pt-32 lg:pt-36 pb-10 sm:pb-14 md:pb-20 lg:pb-28">
    {/* 단일 컬럼 - 원장 사진은 About 페이지에 위치, 메인은 활자 중심 */}
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div
        data-reveal
        class="text-[10px] sm:text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] sm:tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-green-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6"
        style="font-family: var(--font-display);"
      >
        {CLINIC.address.addressLocality} · 한의원
      </div>

      <h1
        data-reveal
        data-reveal-delay="1"
        class="text-[1.85rem] sm:text-[2.4rem] md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.6rem] font-bold text-stone-900 leading-[1.2] md:leading-[1.15] tracking-tight"
      >
        환자의 말을 듣고,
        <br />
        <span class="font-serif italic text-green-900 mr-2">통증의 본질</span>을 찾습니다.
      </h1>

      <p
        data-reveal
        data-reveal-delay="2"
        class="mt-5 sm:mt-7 md:mt-9 text-[17px] md:text-xl text-stone-700 leading-[1.8] md:leading-[1.85] max-w-xl"
      >
        서조혁 원장은 매주 일요일 서울로 새 치료법을 연구하러 다닙니다. 골타·추나·매선·약침·한약을 환자의 체질과 증상에 맞게 결합합니다.
      </p>

      {/* CTA - green-800 + inline color 명시 (Tailwind text-white 누락 방지) */}
      <div
        data-reveal
        data-reveal-delay="3"
        class="mt-7 sm:mt-9 md:mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row flex-wrap gap-3"
      >
        {CLINIC.naverPlaceUrl ? (
          <a
            href={CLINIC.naverPlaceUrl}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            style="color:#ffffff;background-color:#15803d;"
            class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:bg-green-900 font-semibold px-7 py-4 text-[17px] md:text-lg shadow-lg shadow-green-950/20 transition-all"
          >
            <span style="color:#ffffff;">진료 예약</span>
            <span aria-hidden="true" style="color:#ffffff;" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
          </a>
        ) : (
          <a
            href="/visit/"
            style="color:#ffffff;background-color:#15803d;"
            class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:bg-green-900 font-semibold px-7 py-4 text-[17px] md:text-lg shadow-lg shadow-green-950/20 transition-all"
          >
            <span style="color:#ffffff;">오시는길·진료시간</span>
            <span aria-hidden="true" style="color:#ffffff;" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
          </a>
        )}
        <a
          href="/about/"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-transparent border border-stone-300 hover:bg-stone-100 text-stone-800 font-semibold px-7 py-4 text-[17px] md:text-lg transition-all"
        >
          원장 진료 철학
        </a>
      </div>

      {/* 진료시간 미니 - 시니어 친화 크기 */}
      <dl class="mt-10 sm:mt-12 grid grid-cols-[max-content_1fr] gap-x-6 sm:gap-x-10 gap-y-3.5 text-[16px] md:text-lg border-t border-stone-200 pt-7 max-w-md">
        <dt class="text-stone-500 font-medium">평일 (월~금)</dt>
        <dd class="text-stone-900 font-medium tabular-nums">09:30 - 19:00</dd>
        <dt class="text-stone-500 font-medium">토요일</dt>
        <dd class="text-stone-900 font-medium tabular-nums">09:30 - 13:00</dd>
        <dt class="text-stone-500 font-medium">일·공휴일</dt>
        <dd class="text-stone-500">휴진</dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
